summary: September 22 is the 265th day of the year  in the Gregorian calendar.
full_text:
September 22 is the 265th day of the year  in the Gregorian calendar. There are 100 days remaining until the end of the year.
It is frequently the day of the autumnal equinox in the Northern Hemisphere and the day of the vernal equinox in the Southern Hemisphere.
title: September 22
